   Melley joined the AP in Boston in 1996 from the Springfield,
Mass., Union-News and Sunday Republican. He is a native of Amherst,
Mass., and a graduate of the University of Massachusetts in
Amherst.
</P>
<P>
   Melley, 34, succeeds Christine Hanley, who has joined the San
Francisco staff.
