Identix Inc., down 4 1/16 at 17~
</P>
<P>
   The fingerprint-identification company Identix Inc. expects to
lose 12 cents to 15 cents a share in its fiscal third quarter,
worse than analysts' estimates of 10 cents a share. Identix cited
delays in shipping a new, miniature fingerprint scanner.
