Gore for 30 days in a row,'' the release said, referring to an
e-mail challenge sent last month to the Texas governor.
</P>
<P>
   The campaigns failed to mention the most important number: 208.
</P>
<P>
   That's how many days until Nov. 7 -- Election Day.
